{
  "description": "A stunning golden hour photograph depicts a bridge stretching across a body of water, with a bright, large sun dominating the upper portion of the frame. The sun appears as a hazy orb, casting a warm, orange glow across the entire scene. The bridge is silhouetted against the light, appearing as a delicate structure connecting landmasses on either side. Below the bridge, there's visible boat traffic creating white wakes in the water. A distant shoreline with hills provides a backdrop. The water's surface reflects the warm light, creating a shimmering effect. The foreground includes a blurred coastline with some greenery. The overall composition is serene and dramatic, capturing the beauty of a sunset over a coastal landscape.",
